Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.53,0:00:12.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.07,0:00:14.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.90,0:00:16.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅行高興嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.16,0:00:17.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.93,0:00:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早苗阿姨 下次要跟我約會哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.78,0:00:21.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.54,0:00:24.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這次跟說好的不一樣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.36,0:00:27.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本來還很期待著跟早苗阿姨一起去旅行的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.84,0:00:30.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙 別糾纏別人的老婆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.38,0:00:31.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿秋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.08,0:00:35.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然 約會的時候也會帶上汐 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.54,0:00:36.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.29,0:00:37.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就讓我也參加吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.97,0:00:40.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們三人好好玩一玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.23,0:00:41.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋也 汐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.62,0:00:43.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別把我排除在外啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.47,0:01:12.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.46,0:01:15.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋也
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.75,0:01:20.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點也沒變吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.13,0:01:24.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這房間還保持著你們結婚時的狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.05,0:01:27.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 一點也沒變呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.06,0:01:29.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 要帶走嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.96,0:01:32.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我指那個布偶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.02,0:01:35.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐也很喜歡那個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.01,0:01:41.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼長的時間 真是對不起你們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.56,0:01:42.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.56,0:01:44.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直把汐推給你們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.19,0:01:49.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能找到身為父親的責任和義務
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.53,0:01:51.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也全都是靠了早苗阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.89,0:01:54.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼也沒做哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.83,0:01:57.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的把她培養成了一個好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.29,0:01:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都不知道該如何道謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.76,0:02:02.17,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 接下來模仿江川吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.27,0:02:03.65,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,江川
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.37,0:02:08.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 接下來我會靠自己來好好撫養她
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.94,0:02:12.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把她培養成和渚一樣既為別人著想 又堅強的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.10,0:02:20.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋生和我為了渚而換工作 也是在渚五歲的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.62,0:02:22.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.13,0:02:26.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會用一生來報答這份恩情的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.47,0:02:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 就請你們幸福哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.25,0:02:36.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一定會幸福的 跟汐一起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.42,0:02:37.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.38,0:02:39.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.18,0:02:44.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 汐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.98,0:02:46.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿秋說打棒球
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.28,0:02:50.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.62,0:02:52.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.84,0:02:57.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像條死魚一樣的傢伙復活了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.79,0:02:59.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別廢話了 快投吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.55,0:03:04.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐 好好記住你老爸的醜態哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.09,0:03:05.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.19,0:03:07.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐認為哪邊會贏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.61,0:03:08.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿秋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.73,0:03:09.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.51,0:03:13.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子可是看著我的英姿長大的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.65,0:03:16.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 看我怎麼打敗你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.24,0:03:18.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可笑至極
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.04,0:03:28.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.55,0:03:29.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了嗎 汐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.96,0:03:35.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又得去道歉了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.47,0:05:34.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早苗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.35,0:05:37.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也沒資格說別人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.18,0:05:40.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那天起就再也沒哭過
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.29,0:05:44.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真清楚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.98,0:05:48.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那當然了 你當我是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.42,0:05:52.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我有了自己的目標
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.65,0:05:55.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我必須要去養育汐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.00,0:06:01.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以真太好了 沒有迷失了自我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.19,0:06:03.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五年嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.91,0:06:07.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了汐我們才有了寄托呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.01,0:06:10.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 沒錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.75,0:06:13.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這下也終於結束了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.12,0:06:14.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.82,0:06:19.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼長的時間真是辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.48,0:06:22.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裏 我們是一家人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.50,0:06:25.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.21,0:06:27.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.32,0:06:30.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.34,0:06:33.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次該你好好哭一場了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.86,0:06:34.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋生…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.34,0:06:37.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得撐不下去的時候 還有我在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.49,0:06:40.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你哭完之前 我都會在你身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.59,0:06:43.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 已經可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.94,0:07:16.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我們就走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.23,0:07:17.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.45,0:07:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.63,0:07:20.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 去叼了回來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.51,0:07:21.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.17,0:07:23.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也能聽懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.34,0:07:27.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天開始就要跟爸爸一起住了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.32,0:07:28.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要做個乖孩子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.87,0:07:29.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.25,0:07:33.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後我因為工作下班遲了的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.34,0:07:35.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幼兒園的接送還得拜託你們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.64,0:07:37.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 全交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.61,0:07:40.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋也 關於那邊的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.87,0:07:43.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.84,0:07:46.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打算最近就過去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.29,0:07:53.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您的情況我從古河小姐那裏聽說了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.90,0:07:56.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後還請多多關照了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.32,0:07:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼此彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.26,0:08:01.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 汐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.64,0:08:03.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸去工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.45,0:08:05.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 慢走 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.76,0:08:07.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.57,0:08:16.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 那個人就是岡崎先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.97,0:08:18.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以來都幹什麼去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.23,0:08:22.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是跟古河家發生過什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.19,0:08:23.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家庭糾紛？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.35,0:08:26.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是以前的我肯定會發飆了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.70,0:08:30.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 我是岡崎 是岡崎汐的父親
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.45,0:08:32.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.57,0:08:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.45,0:08:38.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為一些原因 一直都把女兒托付給了妻子的娘家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.49,0:08:43.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從今天起我們就要一起住了 還請多多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.67,0:08:46.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 您太客氣了 我們才是請你多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.32,0:08:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家的孩子 跟小汐也很要好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.24,0:08:52.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多多關照了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.14,0:08:53.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.34,0:08:55.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們要住在一起了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.12,0:08:59.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 一直以來勞煩您為我們擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.74,0:09:01.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是會很辛苦的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.43,0:09:03.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要一個人帶大一個小孩子的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.75,0:09:08.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的時期已經由早苗阿姨和大叔代為照顧了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.90,0:09:10.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以從今往後無論如何辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.08,0:09:13.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和他們的辛苦比起來 都算不了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.15,0:09:16.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有什麼困難 隨時可以來找我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.60,0:09:20.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公司也會盡力幫忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.18,0:09:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 恕我冒昧…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.59,0:09:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.60,0:09:28.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐 我來接你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.36,0:09:30.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.47,0:09:34.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然現在是夏季保育中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.11,0:09:37.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是小汐班級的班主任請假了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.56,0:09:39.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請假是因為生病了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.78,0:09:42.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她去參加保育士的研修會了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.77,0:09:44.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下周就回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.67,0:09:47.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來後 請重新和她打聲招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.70,0:09:48.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.53,0:09:51.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的老師是個怎麼樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.32,0:09:55.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭髮長長的 既漂亮又溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.33,0:10:00.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 爸爸要回去工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.43,0:10:04.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有外人來了 不可以開門的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.96,0:10:05.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.11,0:10:08.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事的話就給早苗阿姨打電話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.03,0:10:11.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電話你會打吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.42,0:10:12.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.89,0:10:15.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會在天黑前回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.28,0:10:15.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.74,0:10:17.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.69,0:10:19.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走好 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.05,0:10:46.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.92,0:10:47.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.96,0:10:50.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩隻手拿滿了行李 幫我開一下門
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.09,0:10:58.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從古河家拿過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.43,0:11:02.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糰子大家族和你的換洗衣服 還有玩具什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.36,0:11:04.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先把這個放好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.98,0:11:07.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放哪裏比較好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.44,0:11:13.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.80,0:11:15.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 就放那兒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.70,0:11:25.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸會做飯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.22,0:11:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從現在開始會慢慢去學的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.77,0:11:29.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們兩個人一起學吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.40,0:11:30.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.22,0:11:33.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岡崎先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.89,0:11:39.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公子小姐 好久不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.69,0:11:41.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好幾年不見了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.27,0:11:43.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.62,0:11:45.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是我的女兒 叫汐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.31,0:11:47.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐 快打招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.61,0:11:49.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.28,0:11:53.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 我叫芳野公子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.02,0:11:57.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子就是小渚的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.05,0:11:59.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.85,0:12:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她也一定能成為像小渚那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.56,0:12:06.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堅強又討人喜歡的女性吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.94,0:12:09.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能這樣就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.71,0:12:11.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她以前是媽媽的老師哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.28,0:12:15.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 我聽芳野先生說了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.25,0:12:18.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您妹妹出院了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.71,0:12:19.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.26,0:12:24.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 雖然醫生說這是奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.34,0:12:26.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我們一直都堅信著她會醒過來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.14,0:12:30.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實今天是和妹妹一起出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.74,0:12:33.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小風
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.22,0:12:44.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快打招呼 他們是姐姐的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.87,0:12:49.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就是您的妹妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.77,0:13:01.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您妹妹真有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.02,0:13:03.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小風 沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.81,0:13:06.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是姐姐的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.29,0:13:08.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是我妹妹風子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.49,0:13:12.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這兩位是岡崎先生和小汐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.23,0:13:13.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.68,0:13:15.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 初次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.40,0:13:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.82,0:13:21.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.41,0:13:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太可愛了 我能抱她嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.91,0:13:27.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你一說完就抱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.70,0:13:30.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小風 不能這樣哦 太沒禮貌了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.15,0:13:34.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 她就是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.75,0:13:36.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她多大了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.53,0:13:38.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和岡崎先生同齡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.96,0:13:41.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是因為一直昏迷著
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.36,0:13:45.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以她本人的感覺還只是高中一年級
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.83,0:13:48.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 感覺和汐沒多大區別嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.59,0:13:53.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 姐姐和岡崎先生太失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.17,0:13:56.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生氣了 所以這孩子就是風子的妹妹了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.19,0:13:59.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說莫名其妙的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.43,0:14:01.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁亂也不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.94,0:14:02.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.85,0:14:05.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗚 真是太可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.31,0:14:11.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有點怪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.87,0:14:14.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是交到了新朋友真是太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.15,0:14:14.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.23,0:14:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐 爸爸明天也請假了 我們一起出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.57,0:14:21.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又去旅行？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.59,0:14:23.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.99,0:14:32.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也喜歡糰子大家族嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.46,0:14:34.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早苗說過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.46,0:14:36.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是媽媽的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.97,0:14:37.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.45,0:14:39.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好香
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.77,0:15:00.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.91,0:15:20.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 是朋也君啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.63,0:15:32.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.15,0:15:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.92,0:15:36.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老了很多啊 老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.61,0:15:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.57,0:15:42.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是你的孫女
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.94,0:15:46.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.10,0:15:48.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.08,0:15:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直待在家裏嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.98,0:15:55.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.60,0:15:59.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我見過你的母親了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.79,0:16:03.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和她一起去旅行的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.92,0:16:05.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那北方的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.97,0:16:09.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你以前帶我去過的那個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.47,0:16:09.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.55,0:16:13.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說了很多事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.47,0:16:16.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得你過去很辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.39,0:16:19.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想起了很多…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.06,0:16:21.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.97,0:16:26.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.37,0:16:28.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你累了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.32,0:16:33.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多也該休息一下了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.62,0:16:36.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家鄉去怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.77,0:16:38.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的媽媽在那等著你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.28,0:16:43.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你牽著我的手 發誓要自己把我撫養成人的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.62,0:16:47.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.52,0:16:51.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經足夠努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.79,0:16:53.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 去休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.60,0:16:58.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到家鄉去 陪著你的母親一起生活
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.64,0:16:59.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.64,0:17:20.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經… 可以了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.70,0:17:21.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.24,0:17:25.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經 完成了自己的使命了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.31,0:17:42.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是犧牲了自己的一切 養育我到今天了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.72,0:17:46.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了我這樣沒出息的兒子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.26,0:17:49.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耗費了自己的一生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.30,0:17:52.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.08,0:17:56.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.57,0:18:01.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不覺地 我已經完成了自己的使命了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.70,0:18:07.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真是 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.96,0:18:13.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.29,0:18:36.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,替換的衣服…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.64,0:18:39.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一點不多的錢 我幫你放進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.66,0:18:41.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.82,0:18:44.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊就由我去聯繫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.87,0:18:47.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在路上別把行李弄丟哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.48,0:18:49.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我會小心的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.60,0:18:52.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個家的問題我會想辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.36,0:18:54.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,債務問題也會妥善解決的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.38,0:18:57.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.16,0:18:59.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐 來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.56,0:19:00.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和爺爺說拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.28,0:19:03.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜了 爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.01,0:19:12.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 就此告別了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.53,0:19:15.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多注意下身體
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.77,0:19:16.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.45,0:19:20.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酒別喝太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.97,0:19:21.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.50,0:19:24.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋也
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.54,0:19:26.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看 是零食哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.05,0:19:28.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煙也別抽太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.44,0:19:29.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.73,0:19:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸又要出去了 你別吃太多了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.30,0:19:36.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要健康長壽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.19,0:19:39.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是讓你那麼寂寞 抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.74,0:19:42.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會去報恩的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.45,0:19:45.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我回來後 好好給你做晚飯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.01,0:19:47.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會去…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.06,0:19:49.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們倆一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.78,0:19:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不好 朋也
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.75,0:20:06.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 朋也
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.15,0:20:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼哭了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.91,0:20:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 汐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.63,0:20:25.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心我的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.64,0:20:30.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.90,0:20:33.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以來 謝謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.99,0:20:34.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.89,0:20:42.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.63,0:20:44.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 保重
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.43,0:20:46.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋也 你也多保重
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.27,0:20:59.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人的一生是否是幸福的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.01,0:21:04.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在最幸福的時候失去了愛人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.28,0:21:08.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後只剩下了父子兩人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.23,0:21:12.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了我這個不懂得孝順的兒子一直努力著
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.95,0:21:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的人生 是否是幸福的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.67,0:21:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.14,0:21:51.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 汐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.00,0:21:53.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.49,0:21:55.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 太耀眼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.81,0:21:56.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.53,0:23:42.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 汐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.73,0:23:44.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天有客人來找你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.54,0:23:48.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐 你有什麼會玩的遊戲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.58,0:23:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐 跟媽媽說我們出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.77,0:23:53.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 汐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.90,0:23:55.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很危險的 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.97,0:23:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.55,0:24:01.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油啊

